**Strategic summary:**

| Layer | What Exists (fragmented) | What Guild Provides (unified) |
|-------|------------------------|------------------------------|
| Membership | Discord roles, manual spreadsheets | Badge-gated join, dashboard display, role hierarchy |
| Tasks | Dework (separate tool, EVM-only) | Built-in task board scoped per WG, on-chain escrow |
| Budget | Gnosis Safe (EVM-only) | Per-WG budget tracking in dashboard, variance alerts |
| Compensation | Coordinape (separate tool) | Escrow pays on delivery, peer allocation planned |
| Reporting | Forum posts nobody reads | Structured template, monthly to council, on dashboard |
| Voting | Snapshot (EVM-only) | Built-in proposals + CV2 on-chain integration |
| Docs | Notion (separate tool, paid) | Charter + reports stored per WG on dashboard |

**The pitch in one line:** "One dashboard. Join a group. Claim a task. Get paid. File a report. All badge-gated, all Radix-native, all open source."

